lyrics:
[verse]
In the depths of my soul, I search for truth
A journey of self-discovery, a lifelong pursuit
Through shadows and struggles, I strive to break free
Unlocking the potential that lies within me

[chorus]
Rise, embrace the dawn, leave behind the past
Transformed, reborn, ready to surpass
The barriers that bound, the chains that weighed
Each new day, a chance to ascend unafraid
